          %h3#instructions Instructions for authors
          %p(style="text-align: justify")
            The main purpose of the workshop is to exchange recent ideas and reserch in the area of quantum compilation.
            The workshop has no formal proceedings.
            Authors are invited to submit an abstract or a paper, with no restrictions on the format.
            Submission of tool and case-study papers are highly encouraged.
            In case of a positive evaluation, submissions are accepted either as oral or poster presentation to be part of the workshop program.
            All abstracts and papers are distributed only among the participants.  Please submit your papers through EasyChair:
            %a(href="https://easychair.org/conferences/?conf=iwqc18" target="_blank") https://easychair.org/conferences/?conf=iwqc18
